---
export const prerender = true;
---
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Progettazione Residenziale — Studio Terraviva</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Organic shapes -->
  <div class="organic-shapes" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="shape shape-1"></div>
    <div class="shape shape-2"></div>
    <div class="shape shape-3"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Back button -->
  <a href="/portfolio/sito-vetrina" class="back-btn">
    <span class="back-arrow">&larr;</span> Torna a Studio Terraviva
  </a>

  <!-- Nav -->
  <nav class="nav fade-in">
    <div class="nav-logo">Terraviva</div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/portfolio/sito-vetrina#servizi">Servizi</a>
      <a href="/portfolio/sito-vetrina#progetti">Progetti</a>
      <a href="/portfolio/sito-vetrina#chi-siamo">Chi Siamo</a>
      <a href="/portfolio/sito-vetrina#contatti" class="nav-cta">Contattaci</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero fade-in">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-tag">Progettazione Residenziale</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">La tua casa, <span class="text-terracotta">progettata</span><br />su misura per <span class="text-sage">te</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Dal primo sopralluogo alla consegna delle chiavi: accompagniamo ogni fase del tuo progetto con cura, trasparenza e attenzione ai dettagli.</p>
      <div class="hero-price">Da <strong>&euro;3.000</strong></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image fade-in" style="--delay:0.2s">
      <img src="/images/portfolio/vetrina-loft.jpg" alt="Progetto residenziale" loading="eager" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;border-radius:40% 60% 55% 45% / 55% 40% 60% 45%;" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's Included -->
  <section class="included">
    <div class="section-header fade-in">
      <p class="section-tag">Cosa Include</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Un servizio <span class="text-terracotta">completo</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="included-grid">
      <div class="included-card fade-in" style="--delay:0s">
        <div class="included-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0118 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Sopralluogo</h3>
        <p>Visita in loco per analizzare lo stato dell'immobile, il contesto urbanistico e le potenzialit&agrave; dell'area. Rilievo fotografico completo.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="included-card fade-in" style="--delay:0.1s">
        <div class="included-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Rilievo tecnico</h3>
        <p>Misurazione precisa di tutti gli ambienti con strumentazione laser. Produzione di planimetrie e sezioni in scala.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="included-card fade-in" style="--delay:0.2s">
        <div class="included-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Progetto preliminare</h3>
        <p>Due proposte progettuali con planimetrie, render 3D e moodboard. Confronto e scelta della soluzione preferita.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="included-card fade-in" style="--delay:0.3s">
        <div class="included-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M11 4H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-7"/><path d="M18.5 2.5a2.121 2.121 0 013 3L12 15l-4 1 1-4 9.5-9.5z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Progetto definitivo</h3>
        <p>Elaborati tecnici completi: piante, prospetti, sezioni, dettagli costruttivi. Computo metrico estimativo e capitolato.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="included-card fade-in" style="--delay:0.4s">
        <div class="included-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Pratiche edilizie</h3>
        <p>Gestione completa della burocrazia: CILA, SCIA, permesso di costruire. Rapporti con il Comune e gli enti preposti.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="included-card fade-in" style="--delay:0.5s">
        <div class="included-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Direzione lavori</h3>
        <p>Supervisione del cantiere, coordinamento delle imprese, verifica della qualit&agrave; esecutiva. Visite settimanali con report fotografico.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Timeline / Process -->
  <section class="process">
    <div class="section-header fade-in">
      <p class="section-tag">Il Processo</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Dalla prima idea alle <span class="text-sage">chiavi in mano</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item fade-in" style="--delay:0s">
        <div class="timeline-marker">
          <span>1</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h3>Primo incontro</h3>
          <p>Ci conosciamo, ascoltiamo le tue esigenze, visitiamo l'immobile. Definiamo insieme obiettivi, budget e tempistiche. Questo incontro &egrave; gratuito e senza impegno.</p>
          <span class="timeline-duration">1-2 ore</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item fade-in" style="--delay:0.15s">
        <div class="timeline-marker">
          <span>2</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h3>Rilievo e concept</h3>
          <p>Effettuiamo il rilievo tecnico e sviluppiamo due proposte progettuali. Presentiamo render 3D, moodboard e planimetrie per aiutarti a visualizzare il risultato finale.</p>
          <span class="timeline-duration">2-3 settimane</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item fade-in" style="--delay:0.3s">
        <div class="timeline-marker">
          <span>3</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h3>Progetto esecutivo</h3>
          <p>Sviluppiamo gli elaborati tecnici definitivi, il computo metrico e il capitolato. Prepariamo tutta la documentazione per le pratiche edilizie e selezioniamo le imprese.</p>
          <span class="timeline-duration">3-4 settimane</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item fade-in" style="--delay:0.45s">
        <div class="timeline-marker">
          <span>4</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h3>Cantiere</h3>
          <p>Seguiamo il cantiere con visite settimanali, coordinando le imprese e verificando la qualit&agrave; di ogni lavorazione. Ti teniamo aggiornato con report fotografici regolari.</p>
          <span class="timeline-duration">Variabile</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item fade-in" style="--delay:0.6s">
        <div class="timeline-marker">
          <span>5</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h3>Consegna chiavi</h3>
          <p>Collaudo finale, verifica di conformit&agrave; e consegna della documentazione completa. La tua nuova casa &egrave; pronta per essere vissuta.</p>
          <span class="timeline-duration">1 giorno</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Recent Projects -->
  <section class="recent-projects">
    <div class="section-header fade-in">
      <p class="section-tag">Progetti Recenti</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Lavori <span class="text-terracotta">completati</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="projects-grid">
      <div class="project-card fade-in" style="--delay:0s">
        <div class="project-img">
          <img src="/images/portfolio/vetrina-loft.jpg" alt="Villa Riviera" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
        </div>
        <div class="project-info">
          <span class="project-cat">Nuova costruzione</span>
          <h3>Villa Riviera</h3>
          <p class="project-location">Abano Terme (PD)</p>
          <p class="project-desc">Villa bifamiliare di 280 mq su due livelli con giardino privato, piscina interrata e certificazione energetica classe A4.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="project-card fade-in" style="--delay:0.15s">
        <div class="project-img">
          <img src="/images/portfolio/vetrina-garden.jpg" alt="Loft Industriale" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
        </div>
        <div class="project-info">
          <span class="project-cat">Ristrutturazione</span>
          <h3>Loft Industriale</h3>
          <p class="project-location">Padova</p>
          <p class="project-desc">Trasformazione di un ex magazzino di 150 mq in loft residenziale con soppalco in acciaio e vetro, pavimento in resina e travi a vista.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="project-card fade-in" style="--delay:0.3s">
        <div class="project-img">
          <img src="/images/portfolio/vetrina-professional.jpg" alt="Casa sul Colle" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
        </div>
        <div class="project-info">
          <span class="project-cat">Residenziale</span>
          <h3>Casa sul Colle</h3>
          <p class="project-location">Arqu&agrave; Petrarca (PD)</p>
          <p class="project-desc">Recupero di un casale collinare del '700 con ampliamento contemporaneo in pietra locale. Inserimento paesaggistico e giardino terrazzato.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact / Quote Form -->
  <section class="quote-section">
    <div class="quote-inner fade-in">
      <div class="quote-text">
        <p class="section-tag">Richiedi un Preventivo</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Raccontaci il tuo <span class="text-terracotta">progetto</span></h2>
        <p class="quote-desc">Compila il modulo e ti ricontatteremo entro 48 ore per fissare un primo incontro gratuito e senza impegno.</p>
      </div>
      <form class="quote-form" onsubmit="event.preventDefault()">
        <div class="form-row">
          <input type="text" placeholder="Il tuo nome" class="form-input" />
          <input type="email" placeholder="La tua email" class="form-input" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-row">
          <input type="tel" placeholder="Telefono" class="form-input" />
          <select class="form-input form-select">
            <option value="" disabled selected>Tipo di intervento</option>
            <option>Nuova costruzione</option>
            <option>Ristrutturazione</option>
            <option>Ampliamento</option>
            <option>Interior design</option>
            <option>Altro</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <textarea placeholder="Descrivi brevemente il tuo progetto: dove si trova l'immobile, metratura indicativa, tempistiche desiderate..." class="form-input form-textarea"></textarea>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Invia Richiesta</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-inner">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <h3>Studio Terraviva</h3>
        <p>Via Daniele Manin 8, 35122 Padova (PD)<br/>Tel. 049 876 5432 &mdash; info@studioterraviva.it</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="/portfolio/sito-vetrina#servizi">Servizi</a>
        <a href="/portfolio/sito-vetrina#progetti">Progetti</a>
        <a href="/portfolio/sito-vetrina#chi-siamo">Chi Siamo</a>
        <a href="#">Instagram</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="footer-copy">&copy; 2026 Studio Terraviva di Arch. Francesca Moretti &mdash; P.IVA 04123456789 &mdash; Tutti i diritti riservati.</p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('visible');
          observer.unobserve(entry.target);
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.1, rootMargin: '0px 0px -40px 0px' });
    document.querySelectorAll('.fade-in').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
  </script>

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: #faf8f5; color: #2d2a26;
      overflow-x: hidden; line-height: 1.6;
    }

    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #faf8f5; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #c2703e; border-radius: 4px; }

    .text-terracotta { color: #c2703e; }
    .text-sage { color: #7c8c6c; }

    .fade-in {
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px);
      transition: opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1), transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1);
      transition-delay: var(--delay, 0s);
    }
    .fade-in.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    /* Organic shapes */
    .organic-shapes { position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0; pointer-events: none; overflow: hidden; }
    .shape { position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; opacity: 0.06; animation: floatShape 25s ease-in-out infinite; }
    .shape-1 { width: 500px; height: 500px; top: -150px; right: -100px; background: #c2703e; border-radius: 40% 60% 55% 45% / 55% 40% 60% 45%; }
    .shape-2 { width: 400px; height: 400px; bottom: 10%; left: -100px; background: #7c8c6c; border-radius: 55% 45% 40% 60% / 40% 55% 45% 60%; animation-delay: -8s; }
    .shape-3 { width: 300px; height: 300px; top: 40%; right: 10%; background: #c2703e; border-radius: 45% 55% 60% 40% / 60% 45% 55% 40%; animation-delay: -15s; }
    @keyframes floatShape {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg); }
      33% { transform: translate(30px, -20px) rotate(5deg); }
      66% { transform: translate(-20px, 15px) rotate(-3deg); }
    }

    /* Back button */
    .back-btn {
      position: fixed; top: 24px; left: 24px; z-index: 100;
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 20px; background: rgba(250,248,245,0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border: 1px solid rgba(194,112,62,0.15);
      border-radius: 50px; color: #c2703e; text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500; transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .back-btn:hover { background: rgba(194,112,62,0.08); border-color: rgba(194,112,62,0.4); box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(194,112,62,0.1); }
    .back-arrow { transition: transform 0.3s ease; }
    .back-btn:hover .back-arrow { transform: translateX(-3px); }

    /* Nav */
    .nav {
      position: relative; z-index: 10;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px 24px 0;
    }
    .nav-logo { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; color: #2d2a26; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links a { color: #6b6560; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: color 0.3s ease; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: #c2703e; }
    .nav-cta { padding: 8px 20px !important; background: #c2703e !important; color: #fff !important; border-radius: 50px; }

    /* Sections common */
    .section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px; }
    .section-tag { font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #c2703e; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .section-title { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 400; color: #2d2a26; }

    /* Hero */
    .hero {
      position: relative; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 60px; align-items: center;
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 24px 100px;
    }
    .hero-tag { font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #c2703e; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4.5vw, 3.4rem); line-height: 1.15;
      font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 24px; color: #2d2a26;
    }
    .hero-sub { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 300; color: #8a847e; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 24px; max-width: 480px; }
    .hero-price {
      display: inline-block; padding: 12px 28px; border-radius: 50px;
      background: rgba(194,112,62,0.08); border: 1.5px solid rgba(194,112,62,0.2);
      color: #c2703e; font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    .hero-price strong { font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; }

    /* Included */
    .included { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 24px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .included-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
    .included-card {
      padding: 32px; border-radius: 20px; background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #ede8e3; transition: all 0.4s ease;
    }
    .included-card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(194,112,62,0.1); border-color: rgba(194,112,62,0.2); }
    .included-icon {
      width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(194,112,62,0.08); color: #c2703e;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .included-card h3 { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .included-card p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #8a847e; line-height: 1.7; }

    /* Timeline */
    .process { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 24px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .timeline { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; padding-left: 48px; }
    .timeline::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; left: 20px; top: 0; bottom: 0;
      width: 2px; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #c2703e, #7c8c6c);
    }
    .timeline-item { position: relative; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .timeline-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .timeline-marker {
      position: absolute; left: -48px; top: 0;
      width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: #c2703e; color: #fff;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 400;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .timeline-content {
      padding: 24px; border-radius: 16px; background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #ede8e3; transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .timeline-content:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(194,112,62,0.08); border-color: rgba(194,112,62,0.2); }
    .timeline-content h3 { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .timeline-content p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #8a847e; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .timeline-duration {
      display: inline-block; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;
      color: #7c8c6c; background: rgba(124,140,108,0.1);
      padding: 3px 12px; border-radius: 20px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }

    /* Recent Projects */
    .recent-projects {
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 24px;
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
    }
    .projects-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 28px; }
    .project-card {
      border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #ede8e3; transition: all 0.4s ease;
    }
    .project-card:hover { transform: translateY(-8px); box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(194,112,62,0.1); }
    .project-img { height: 200px; overflow: hidden; }
    .project-img img { transition: transform 0.6s ease; }
    .project-card:hover .project-img img { transform: scale(1.05); }
    .project-info { padding: 24px; }
    .project-cat {
      display: inline-block; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: #c2703e; background: rgba(194,112,62,0.08);
      padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .project-info h3 { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .project-location { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #7c8c6c; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .project-desc { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #8a847e; line-height: 1.6; }

    /* Quote Section */
    .quote-section {
      background: #f5f0eb; padding: 100px 24px; position: relative; z-index: 1;
    }
    .quote-inner {
      max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: start;
    }
    .quote-desc { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #8a847e; line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 16px; }
    .quote-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
    .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    .form-input {
      padding: 14px 18px; border: 1.5px solid #ddd6cd; border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 0.9rem; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: #fff; transition: border-color 0.3s ease; outline: none;
      color: #2d2a26;
    }
    .form-input:focus { border-color: #c2703e; }
    .form-select { appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #8a847e; }
    .form-textarea { min-height: 120px; resize: vertical; }
    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-block; padding: 14px 36px;
      background: #c2703e; color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 50px; border: none; cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(194,112,62,0.25); }

    /* Footer */
    .footer { padding: 60px 24px 30px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .footer-inner {
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start;
      padding-bottom: 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ede8e3;
    }
    .footer-brand h3 { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .footer-brand p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #8a847e; line-height: 1.6; }
    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; }
    .footer-links a { color: #8a847e; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; transition: color 0.3s; }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: #c2703e; }
    .footer-copy { max-width: 1100px; margin: 16px auto 0; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #bbb5ae; }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .included-grid, .projects-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; padding: 100px 24px 60px; }
      .included-grid, .projects-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .quote-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
      .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .footer-inner { flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
      .back-btn { top: 12px; left: 12px; font-size: 0.78rem; padding: 8px 14px; }
      .timeline { padding-left: 40px; }
      .timeline::before { left: 16px; }
      .timeline-marker { left: -40px; width: 32px; height: 32px; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .hero-title { font-size: 1.8rem; }
    }
  </style>
</body>
